        name: `Fine Arts Center Spring Dance Concert`,
        sort_time: "2026-04-16 19:00:00",
        end_time_formatted: "2026-04-16 23:59",
        detail: "Join us for an inspiring evening of dance performed by the talented students of the Fine Arts Center Dance Program. The performance features a dynamic and diverse repertoire choreographed by faculty members Gina Buntz and Anita Pacylowski, alongside distinguished guest artists Jacquelyn Callé, Alonzo King, Anindo Marshall, and Janice Rosario. The evening will also highlight original student choreography created by members of the Class of 2026.",
